## Pointers

**Installation**
* npm install
* or
* yarn install

**Run application**
* npm start
* npm run dev (To run via nodemon)

**End Points**
* Base Url: http://localhost:5000/v0
* Get Product(GET): /product?id=1&currency=CAD (e.g.: http://localhost:5000/v0/product?id=1&currency=CAD)
* List Product(POST): /product (e.g.: http://localhost:5000/v0/product)
* - Payload ^ 
* { "page": 1, "limit": 10, "currency": "USD" }